statements: SELECT * FROM fashion_photography_trends;
SELECT trend_name, trend_description FROM fashion_photography_trends WHERE industry_preference_level > 3;
SELECT trend_id, trend_name FROM fashion_photography_trends WHERE industry_preference_level = 5;
SELECT * FROM fashion_photography_trends WHERE trend_name LIKE 'Vintage%';
SELECT trend_name, industry_preference_level FROM fashion_photography_trends WHERE trend_id IN (2, 4);
SELECT * FROM fashion_photography_trends WHERE industry_preference_level > 3 ORDER BY trend_id DESC, trend_name ASC;
SELECT trend_name, industry_preference_level FROM fashion_photography_trends WHERE industry_preference_level BETWEEN 1 AND 5 ORDER BY industry_preference_level DESC;
SELECT trend_name, trend_description FROM fashion_photography_trends WHERE trend_name LIKE '%vintage%' OR trend_name LIKE '%retro%';
SELECT * FROM fashion_photography_trends WHERE industry_preference_level IN (3, 4, 5) AND trend_description IS NOT NULL ORDER BY industry_preference_level DESC;
SELECT trend_id, trend_name FROM fashion_photography_trends WHERE industry_preference_level < 3 OR industry_preference_level > 6;
SELECT * FROM fashion_photography_trends;
SELECT trend_name, publication_date FROM fashion_photography_trends WHERE publication_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT id, trend_name, trend_description FROM fashion_photography_trends ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT photographer_name, style_name, photo_url FROM style_tracking WHERE photographer_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT * FROM style_tracking ORDER BY tracking_date ASC, id DESC;
SELECT * FROM fashion_photography_trends WHERE publication_date >= '2020-01-01';
SELECT trend_name, trend_description FROM fashion_photography_trends WHERE id = 3;
SELECT style_name, photographer_name, photo_url FROM style_tracking WHERE tracking_date < '2021-06-15' ORDER BY tracking_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM fashion_photography_trends WHERE trend_name LIKE '%vintage%';
SELECT trend_name, COUNT(id) AS total_trends FROM fashion_phjsony_trends GROUP BY trend_name HAVING COUNT(id) > 1;
SELECT * FROM fashion_trends;
SELECT trend_name, start_date, end_date FROM fashion_trends WHERE trend_id = 2;
SELECT description, start_date FROM fashion_trends WHERE trend_id = 1 ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM photography_styles WHERE photographer_name IS NOT NULL;
SELECT style_id, style_name, creation_date FROM photography_styles ORDER BY creation_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM fashion_trends;
SELECT trend_id, trend_name, start_date, end_date FROM fashion_trends WHERE start_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT trend_name, description FROM fashion_trends WHERE end_date <= '2023-01-01' ORDER BY trend_name ASC;
SELECT style_name, description, photographer_name FROM photography_styles WHERE creation_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY style_name DESC;

SELECT preference_id, trend_name, style_name, preference_score FROM industry_preferences INNER JOIN fashion_trends ON industry_preferences.trend_id = fashion_trends.trend_id INNER JOIN photography_styles ON industry_preferences.style_id = photography_styles.style_id WHERE preference_score > 0.5 ORDER BY preference_score DESC, trend_name ASC;
SELECT trend_name, trend_description FROM Trends;
SELECT style_name, popularity_score FROM Styles ORDER BY popularity_score DESC;
SELECT trend_name, trend_description FROM Trends WHERE trend_id < 5;
SELECT * FROM Preferences WHERE style_id = 3;
SELECT direction_name, direction_description FROM CreativeDirection ORDER BY direction_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM Styles WHERE popularity_score > 0.5;
SELECT trend_name, trend_description FROM Trends ORDER BY trend_name ASC;
SELECT style_name, popularity_score FROM Styles WHERE style_id IN (1, 3, 5);
SELECT cd.direction_name, s.style_name, t.trend_name FROM CreativeDirection cd JOIN Styles s ON cd.style_id = s.style_id JOIN Trends t ON cd.trend_id = t.trend_id;
SELECT p.preference_id, s.style_name, t.trend_name FROM Preferences p JOIN Styles s ON p.style_id = s.style_id JOIN Trends t ON p.trend_id = t.trend_id ORDER BY p.preference_id DESC;
